  "texts": [
    "In integrated DevOps and continuous testing environments, AI-generated test data becomes the foundation for consistent, efficient, and autonomous test execution.",
    "By combining the strengths of logical accuracy (constraints), behavioral realism (GANs), and exploratory robustness (fuzzing), organizations can build comprehensive test suites that accelerate release cycles while enhancing system resilience.",
    "The goal of this comparative evaluation is to quantify and qualify the impact of Artificial Intelligence (AI) integration into Quality Assurance (QA) processes.",
    "Specifically, the comparison focuses on two fundamental QA approaches:",
    " Traditional QA: Manual or semi-automated test case design, manual test data preparation, and rulebased execution."
  ],
